et%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erender%20software%20engineers%20irrelevant%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20materially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-ladder-software-engineers-collapsing-ai-google-meta-coding-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecut%20down%20on%20job%20openings%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20field%20%E2%80%94%20Chennapragada%20believes%20that%20AI%20only%20adds%20a%20further%20layer%20of%20abstraction%20in%20the%20existing%20process%20of%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20program%20in%20assembly%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20us%20don't%20even%20program%20in%20C%2C%20and%20then%20you're%20kind%20of%20higher%20and%20higher%20layers%20of%20abstraction.%20So%20to%20me%2C%20they%20will%20be%20ways%20that%20you%20will%20tell%20the%20computer%20what%20to%20do%2C%20right%3F%20It'll%20just%20be%20at%20a%20much%20higher%20level%20of%20abstraction%2C%20which%20is%20great.%20It%20democratizes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChennapragada%20said%20it's%20possible%20that%2C%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we'll%20think%20of%20software%20engineers%20more%20as%20software%20operators%2C%20but%20the%20role%20itself%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwindsurf-ceo-ai-hiring-software-engineers-productivity-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunlikely%20to%20disappear%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere'll%20be%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%20more%20software%20operators%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20'Cs%2C'%20maybe%20we'll%20have%20'SOs%2C'%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20don't%20understand%20computer%20science%20and%20it's%20a%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20it's%20a%20mental%20model.%20So%20I%20strongly%20disagree%20with%20the%20whole%2C%20'Coding%20is%20dead.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20fate%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropbox-product-vp-advice-to-product-managers-ai-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproject%20managers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0who%20are%20subject%2C%20like%20many%20other%20middle%20managers%2C%20to%20big%20tech's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-amazon-google-embrace-flatter-structure-fewer-managers-boost-efficiency-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20flattening%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20Chennapragada%20expects%20them%20to%20endure%2C%20albeit%20with%20modified%20responsibilities.%20Taste%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20be%20more%20important%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20sense%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20supply%20of%20ideas%2C%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20supply%20of%20ideas%20in%20prototypes%2C%20which%20is%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Chennapragada%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20raises%20the%20floor%2C%20but%20it%20raises%20the%20ceiling%20as%20well.%20In%20some%20sense%2C%20how%20do%20you%20break%20out%20in%20these%20times%20that%20you%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20is%20something%20that%20rises%20above%20the%20noise%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChennapragada%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%20prior%20to%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20makes%20it%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20actualize%20an%20idea%2C%20she%20said%2C%20which%20means%20that%20sifting%20through%20the%20glut%20of%20ideas%20will%20be%20especially%20important%20%E2%80%94%20so%20project%20managers%20will%20need%20to%20further%20develop%20what%20Chennapragada%20calls%20%26quot%3Bthe%20taste-making%20and%20the%20editing%26quot%3B%20instincts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20world%20where%20the%20supply%20of%20ideas%2C%20supply%20of%20prototypes%20becomes%20even%20more%20like%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%20higher%2C%20you'd%20have%20to%20think%20about%2C%20'What%20is%20the%20editing%20function%20here%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20it's%20so%20much%20easi