Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20about%20humor%2C%20aesthetics%2C%20or%20just%20jumping%20on%20a%20trend%2C%20everyone's%20coming%20at%20it%20from%20a%20different%20angle%2C%26quot%3B%20Kanaprach%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%2C%20to%20me%2C%20makes%20this%20whole%20thing%20more%20than%20just%20a%20'fake%20toy'%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Pop%20Mart%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221978469b-8a07-4988-a943-44be7657312d%5C%22%3EA%20cheaper%2C%20funnier%20alternative%20to%20Labubu%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20fake%20Labubu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68302cc3ca50259add4cddfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20obvious%20defects%20with%20my%20Lafufu.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELafufu%20buyers%20told%20me%20they%20love%20the%20fakes%20because%20of%20how%20ugly%20they%20are%2C%20not%20in%20spite%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiabella%20Rivera%2C%20a%20college%20freshman%20from%20San%20Diego%2C%20said%20she%20got%20a%20Lafufu%20for%20%2412%20because%20the%20real%20ones%20were%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%20to%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Lafufu%20came%20without%20eyes%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20superglue%20them%20on%2C%20but%20it%20still%20turned%20out%20really%20cute%2C%26quot%3B%20Rivera%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenn%20Lazzerin%2C%20who%20works%20at%20an%20elementary%20school%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20as%20a%20behavior%20analyst%2C%20has%20two%20Lafufus.%20The%20first%20was%20an%20unintentional%20buy%20%E2%80%94%20she%20was%20scammed%20by%20an%20online%20seller%20claiming%20the%20doll%20was%20authentic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20soon%20after%2C%20she%20bought%20a%20second%20Lafufu%20knowingly%2C%20because%20of%20how%20ugly%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20eyes%20pop%20out%2C%20it%20has%20blush%20blindness%2C%20and%20the%20teeth%20are%20misprinted%2C%26quot%3B%20Lazzerin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fake%20Labubu%20offers%20a%20different%20serotonin%20rush%20than%20getting%20an%20original.%20It's%20like%2C%20how%20ugly%20can%20it%20get%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhong%2C%20the%20trends%20manager%2C%20said%20fakes%20can%20often%20look%20more%20eccentric%20or%20intriguing%20than%20real%20Labubus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20anyone%20with%20enough%20money%20can%20buy%20a%20'real%20Labubu'%20straight%20from%20the%20store%2C%20a%20rare%2C%20well-made%20fake%20with%20a%20unique%20outfit%20or%20expression%20might%20require%20more%20taste%2C%20effort%2C%20or%20insider%20knowledge%20to%20source%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustin%20D'Souza%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Ozzie%20Collectables%2C%20an%20Australian%20collectibles%20store%2C%20said%20Labubus%20are%20made%20with%20high-quality%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAuthentic%20Labubus%20are%20crafted%20with%20care%20and%20creativity%2C%20and%20counterfeit%20versions%20can%20detract%20from%20the%20unique%20experience%20that%20collectors%20seek%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20packaging%20of%20genuine%20products%20typically%20features%20high-quality%20printing%20and%20branding%2C%20whereas%20counterfeit%20packaging%20may%20appear%20less%20polished%20or%20have%20inconsistencies%2C%26quot%3B%20D'Souza%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217c390f1-f250-4da1-a613-20e3677049fe%5C%22%3EBuying%20a%20Lafufu%20has%20convinced%20some%20people%20to%20pick%20up%20real%20Labubus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20look%20at%20collectable%20designer%20art%20toy%20Labubu%20at%20a%20Pop%20Mart%20store%20in%20Siam%20Square%20in%20Bangkok%20on%20May%208%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68302c29c6ad28