i%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20NCL%20Salten%20was%20transporting%20goods%20to%20the%20Norwegian%20town%20of%20Orkanger%20when%20it%20ran%20aground.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ship's%20owner%20said%20it%20had%20run%20aground%20twice%20in%202023%20and%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20440-foot-long%20cargo%20ship%20ran%20aground%20beside%20a%20house%20in%20Byneset%2C%20Norway%2C%20on%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20local%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20ship%20had%20hit%20the%20rocky%20cliff%20right%20next%20to%20it%2C%20it%20would%20have%20lifted%20up%20and%20hit%20the%20house%20hard.%20It%20wasn't%20many%20meters%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Johan%20Helberg%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house%2C%20told%20local%20newspaper%20Nidaros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelberg%20said%20he%20was%20asleep%20when%20the%20ship%20ran%20aground%20and%20did%20not%20know%20what%20happened%20until%20his%20neighbor%20alerted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%2C%20who%20in%20the%20world%20rings%20the%20doorbell%20at%205%3A45%20in%20the%20morning%3F%20I%20looked%20out%20the%20window%2C%20and%20he%20said%3A%20'Haven't%20you%20seen%20the%20ship%3F'%26quot%3B%20Helberg%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2016%20men%20aboard%20the%20NCL%20Salten%2C%20Helberg%20said%20in%20his%20interview%20with%20the%20Times.%20The%20boat%20was%20captained%20by%20a%20Norwegian%2C%20and%20its%20crew%20comprises%20Russians%20and%20Ukrainians%2C%20Helberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelberg%20told%20the%20Times%20that%20his%20neighbor%2C%20Jostein%20J%C3%B8rgensen%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20shock%20all%20day%26quot%3B%20after%20seeing%20the%20ship%20plow%20into%20their%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJ%C3%B8rgensen%20told%20the%20local%20media%20outlet%20TV%202%20that%20he%20heard%20the%20ship%20at%20around%205%20a.m.%20local%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20looked%20out%20the%20window%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20boat%20moving%20at%20full%20speed%20towards%