3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUBS%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20avatar%20videos%20from%20analysts'%20notes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E36%20analysts%20covering%20a%20range%20of%20sectors%20are%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20Swiss%20bank's%20initiative.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUBS%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20clients%20have%20been%20seeking%20more%20video%20options.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBanks%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20save%20their%20analysts'%20time%20while%20giving%20clients%20what%20they%20want.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20uses%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-of-america-artificial-intelligence-tool-banker-assist-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBanker%20Assist%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20aggregate%20information%20to%20offer%20insights%20unique%20to%20each%20client%2C%20while%20Goldman%20Sachs%20has%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-ai-uses-5-tools-employees-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGS%20AI%20Assistant%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20functions%20as%20an%20in-house%20ChatGPT%20for%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwiss%20bank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubs-leadership-investment-banking-wealth-csuite-credit-suisse-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUBS%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20gone%20further%2C%20using%20AI%20to%20generate%20avatars%20of%20analysts%20that%20explain%20their%20research%20to%20clients%2C%20and%20it's%20planning%20to%20do%20this%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swiss%20bank%20started%20using%20AI%20avatars%20of%20some%20analysts%20in%20January.%20About%2036%20UBS%20analysts%2C%20or%205%25%20of%20its%20total%2C%20have%20volunteered%20to%20take%20part.%20They%20cover%20sectors%20including%20technology%2C%20consumer%20goods%2C%20and%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS's%20use%20of%20AI%20avatars%20was%20first%20reported%20by%20The%20Financial%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-jony-ive-io-startup-apple-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Synthesia%20tools%2C%20a%20script%20is%20generated%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20seconds%20that%20is%20then%20edited%20by%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Solomon%2C%20head%20of%20global%20research%20technology%20at%20UBS%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20team%20started%20creating%20videos%20of%20analysts%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20but%20capacity%20restrictions%20meant%20they%20were%20capped%20at%20about%201%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20were%20writing%20an%20average%20of%20two%20notes%20a%20week%20but%20would%20only%20go%20to%20the%20video%20studio%20once%20a%20quarter%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20tools%20are%20%26quot%3Benabling%20somebody%20to%20use%20a%20capability%20in%20video%20that%20they%20weren't%20really%20able%20to%20use%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20gives%20clients%20another%20way%20to%20digest%20information%20and%20meet%20their%20rising%20demand%20for%20video%2C%20Solomon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20compared%20an%20avatar%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20an%20analyst's%20toolkit.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20an%20analyst%20joins%20UBS%2C%20we%20give%20them%20Excel%2C%20we%20give%20them%20our%20authoring%20platform%2C%20we%20give%20them%20a%20CRM%20%5Bcustomer%20relationship%20management%5D%20tool%20so%20they%20can%20talk%20to%20clients.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20have%20an%20avatar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolomon%20said%20the%20next%20step%20would%20be%20integrating%20the%20technology%20so%20that%20a%20video%20can%20eventually%20be%20created%20when%20an%20analyst%20publishes%20a%20note%20%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20need%20for%20editing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20hoped%20this%20would%20become%20possible%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20process%20was%20fully%20automated%2C%20UBS%20said%20analysts%20will%20still%20assess%20a%20video%20based%20on%20their%20notes%20before%20it%20is%20sent%20to%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolomon%20said%20that%20ideally%2C%20the%20avatars%20would%20eventually%20become%20part%20of%20the%20onboarding%20process%2C%20so%20that%20whenever%20a%20note%20is%20published%2C%20there's%20a%20video%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20would%20be%20integrating%20this%20capability%20directly%20into%20the%20authoring%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20script%20generator%2C%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20send%20the%20script%20to%20generate%20the%20avatar%2C%20and%20then%20we%20obviously%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20deliver%20the%20avatar%20to%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Solomon%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20string%20all%20that%20together%20so%20that%20as%20they're%20writing%20the%20note%2C%20they%20can%20get%20the%20video%20with%20it%20as%20well.%20Our%20goal%20is%20absolutely%20not%20to%20do%2050%2C000%20videos%20a%20year%2C%20but%20clearly%20there's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20do%20more%20videos%20than%20we%20are%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-videos-analysts-research-notes-ubs-swiss-bank-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747991330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f4ee76ffb6822ec613cc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-videos-analysts-research-notes-ubs-swiss-bank-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UBS%20is%20using%20OpenAI%20and%20Synthesia%20tools%20to%20generate%20scripts%20from%20analysts'%20research%20notes%20that%20are%20then%20edited.%20It%20aims%20to%20fully%20automate%20the%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nredmond%40insider.com%20(Nora%20Redmond)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-videos-analysts-research-notes-ubs-swiss-bank-2025-5%22%2C