0its%20technology%2C%20which%20about%2025%20companies%20have%20been%20beta%20testing%20since%20late%202024%2C%20has%20been%20used%20across%20engineering%2C%20product%20management%2C%20sales%20marketing%2C%20and%20operations%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ea%20Coworker%20can%20act%20as%20an%20engineering%20teammate%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-boss-ai-junior-coder-within-a-year-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrite%20code%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20create%20and%20review%20pull%20requests%2C%20and%20automate%20release%20notes%2C%20keeping%3C%2Fspan%3E%20human%20developers%20focused%20on%20shipping%20new%20features.%20It%20can%20also%20act%20as%20a%20sales%20teammate%2C%20analyzing%20sales%20calls%20and%20generating%20proposals%20and%20follow-up%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoworker%20uses%20its%20own%20products%20at%20work%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20startup%20a%20leg%20up%20in%20shipping%20new%20features%20and%20developing%20the%20technology%2C%20said%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20Alex%20Calder.%20For%20example%2C%20Coworker's%20agents%20do%20work%20like%20drafting%20product%20requirement%20documents%20based%20on%20customer%20feedback%2C%20creating%20tickets%2C%20writing%20code%2C%20and%20turning%20that%20code%20into%20sales%20talking%20points%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20we've%20seen%20our%20internal%20team%20going%20from%20'AI%20is%20good%20at%20giving%20me%20information'%20to%20'AI%20is%20good%20at%20using%20that%20information%20to%20do%20work%20for%20me'%2C%26quot%3B%20Calder%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20only%20possible%20when%20you%20give%20AI%20really%20rich%20context%20on%20your%20company%2C%20your%20goals%2C%20and%20how%20you%20do%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalder%20and%20his%20cofounder%2C%20Coworker%20chief%20product%20officer%20Bradford%20Church%2C%20are%20former%20Uber