h%20to%20its%20latest%20AI%20models%20and%20wearables%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20packed%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20felt%20electrifying.%20Google%20showed%20impressive%20stats%20about%20how%20its%20AI%20has%20taken%20off.%20It%20had%20plenty%20of%20far-out%20goals%2C%20too%2C%20like%20building%20a%20universal%20AI%20assistant%20and%20extended%20reality%20glasses%20that%20give%20directions%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%2FO%20also%20showcased%20Google's%20vulnerabilities.%20Some%20releases%20clearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-new-ai-updates-overlap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverlapped%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20arch-rival%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-jony-ive-io-startup-apple-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20upstaged%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20a%20big%20announcement%20of%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20conference%20now%20over%2C%20here%20are%20six%20main%20takeaways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bed6191f-e61f-4c01-a9bb-7936a9d71cf5%5C%22%3EGoogle%20wants%20a%20'total%20overhaul'%20of%20Search%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20touted%20at%20I%2FO%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-vision-for-search-in-an-ai-era-gemini-io-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Mode%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20what%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Btotal%20overhaul%26quot%3B%20of%20Google's%20most%20iconic%20feature.%20In%20AI%20Mode%2C%20users%20will%20have%20a%20far%20more%20conversational%20Search%20experience%2C%20asking%20Google%20questions%20directly%20about%20what%20they're%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20marked%20change%20from%20the%20traditional%20experience%20of%20going%20through%20a%20long%20list%20of%20links%20to%20find%20the%20right%20answer%2C%20which%20feels%20more%20clunky%20than%20ever%20in%20an%20age%20of%20AI%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20AI%20features%20like%20these%20could%20cannibalize%20Google%20Search%20and%20threaten%20the%20tech%20giant's%20main%20cash%20cow%2C%20Google%20Ads.%20Google%20risks%20not%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20heavily%20monetize%20these%20AI%20tools.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fads-commerce%2Fgoogle-search-ai-brand-discovery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20testing%3C%2Fa%3E%20ads%20in%20AI%20Mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d879521-dd09-4b0d-bff0-e546768da240%5C%22%3EGemini%20everywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20AI%20model%20family%2C%20Gemini%2C%20took%20center%20stage%20at%20I%2FO.%20Google%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20integrate%20Gemini%20into%20Chrome%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20chat%20with%20its%20latest%20AI%20models%20while%20they%20browse.%20(The%20feature%20rolls%20out%20to%20subscribers%20this%20summer.)%20It's%20a%20shot%20across%20the%20bow%20to%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20already%20has%20a%20popular%20Chrome%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%2FO%20also%20announced%20an%20array%20of%20updates%20to%20its%20Gemini%20app%2C%20which%20recently%20passed%20400%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%20%E2%80%94%20an%20impressive%20figure%2C%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-usage-surging-rivals-chatgpt-meta-dominating-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20behind%3C%2Fa%3E%20ChatGPT.%20With%20an%20update%20called%20Personal%20Context%2C%20Gemini%20app%20users%20can%20get%20tailored%20responses%20based%20on%20personal%20data%20from%20Google%20services%2C%20like%20asking%20its%20AI%20to%20find%20a%20long-lost%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20part%20of%20a%20long-term%20plan%20to%20build%20a%20universal%20AI%20assistant%3A%20what%20Google%20calls%20Project%20Astra.%20While%20it's%20still%20unfinished%2C%20that%20plan%20feels%20more%20fleshed%20out%20now%20than%20when%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-astra-google-ai-agent-dancing-gemini-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etested%20Astra%20a%20year%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f23190f0-6b0a-493a-b6ed-3a4e8eea2d2c%5C%22%3ESoaring%20AI%20traction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20AI%20features%20are%20undeniably%20cool%2C%20though%20Google's%20AI%20traction%20garnered%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20reactions%20at%20Pichai's%20keynote%20speech%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnstage%2C%20Pichai%20boasted%20that%20the%20number%20of%20tokens%20generated%20by%20Google%20across%20all%20its%20platforms%20a%20month%20had%20exploded%2050%20times%20to%20over%20480%20trillion%20since%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20gasped%E2%80%94it%20was%20a%20big%20moment.%20Last%20year's%20I%2FO%20felt%20like%20a%20giant%20teaser%20for%20coming%20AI%20features%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20promise%20but%20little%20to%20show%20for%20it.%20This%20year%20felt%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224022be3a-3ff2-4854-858c-435470e3d803%5C%22%3ESergey%20Brin%20goes%20founder%20mode%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20greater%20manifestation%20of%20Google%20tripling%20down%20on%20AI%20than%20cofounder%20Sergey%20Brin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-cofounder-sergey-brin-ai-io-conference%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrashing%20a%20fireside%20chat%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20DeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis.%20That%20was%20after%20Brin%20wandered%20around%20a%20pavilion%20trying%20on%20a%20pair%20of%20Google's%20XR%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20chat%2C%20Brin%20said%20he%20goes%20into%20the%20office%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20much%20every%20day%20now%26quot%3B%20to%20work%20on%20AI.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20retired%20computer%20scientists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sergey-brin-computer-scientists-should-not-be-retired-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20get%20back%20to%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20current%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sergey-brin-office-work-gemini-ai-research-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrin%20has%20been%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Google%20since%202023%20as%20the%20search%20giant%20races%20against%20AI%20rivals%2C%20and%20it's%20obvious%20he's%20in%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-everyone-in-tech-talking-founder-mode-paul-graham-chesky-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efounder%20mode%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20something%20quite%20rare%20at%20a%20mature%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ec0ba97-5301-4a53-94c8-83ba0b1e5775%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20smart%20glasses%20are%20here%20%E2%80%94%20sort%20of%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20let%20BI%20briefly%20try%20on%20its%20prototype%20Android%20XR%20glasses%2C%20which%20have%20Gemini's%20AI%20features%20and%20allow%20users%20to%20ask%20questions.%20While%20the%20tech%20shows%20promise%2C%20it's%20still%20early%20days.%20Google%20staffers%20asked%20the%20throngs%20of%20I%2FO%20attendees%20lining%20up%20for%20demos%20not%20to%20ask%20about%20price%2C%20availability%2C%20or%20battery%20life.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20know!%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prototype%20glasses%20feel%20impressively%20lightweight%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20too%20much%20so%2C%20to%20the%20point%20that%20they%20felt%20like%20they%20might%20fall%20off%20our%20faces.%20The%20display%20sits%20only%20on%20the%20right%20lens%20and%20is%20practically%20invisible%20unless%20viewed%20at%20just%20the%20right%20angle%20under%20the%20right%20light.%20It's%20full-color%2C%20but%20it's%20small%20and%20subtle%20enough%20that%20you%20might%20miss%20the%20display%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20weren't%20allowed%20to%20view%20Google%20Maps%20or%20Photos%20in%20the%20glasses%20like%20Google%20showed%20off%20in%20its%20keynote.%20Instead%2C%20we%20put%20on%20the%20glasses%20and%20walked%20around%20a%20room%20filled%20with%20artwork%20on%20the%20walls%20and%20travel%20catalogs%20on%20a%20table%20that%20we%20could%20ask%20Gemini%20questions%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gemini%20correctly%20identified%20the%20artwork%2C%20it%20couldn't%20answer%20a%20basic%20travel%20query%20when%20we%20looked%20at%20the%20travel%20catalogs%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20cheapest%20flight%20to%20New%20York%20next%20month%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20because%20the%20display%20is%20only%20on%20one%20side%2C%20focusing%20on%20it%20made%20us%20feel%20a%20bit%20cross-eyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20version%20we%20saw%20isn't%20the%20final%20design.%20It's%20missing%20the%20coming%20Warby%20Parker%20and%20Gentle%20Monster%20flair%2C%20though%20we%20did%20see%20glimmers%20of%20something%20promising%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246f20e82-3be1-47e3-b71d-7d84921cab5e%5C%22%3EThrowing%20everything%20against%20the%20wall%20may%20or%20may%20not%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20announcements%20are%20undeniably%20impressive%2C%20though%20some%20of%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-new-ai-updates-overlap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efelt%20repetitive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20hard%20to%20understand%20the%20difference%20between%20Search%20Live%20and%20Gemini%20Live%2C%20for%20example.%20Both%20of%20them%20involve%20chatting%20with%20your%20phone%20about%20what%20it%20sees%20through%20its%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20strategy%20of%20launching%20literally%20100%20different%20things%20at%20once%20could%20work%20for%20the%20company.%20It%20could%20also%20signal%20a%20lack%20of%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20was%20at%20an%20I%2FO%20panel%20when%20the%20news%20broke%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20buying%20former%20Apple%20design%20chief%20Jony%20Ive's%20hardware%20startup.%20Seeing%20OpenAI%20upstage%20Google%20like%20that%20felt%20a%20little%20ominous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Google%20panel%20BI%20attended%20was%20quite%20dry%20and%20technical%2C%20with%20terms%20like%20AI-powered%20%26quot%3Btool%20calling%26quot%3B%20mentioned%20several%20times.%20The%20contrast%20with%20OpenAI's%20buzzy%20announcement%20couldn't%20be%20clearer.%20We%20even%20saw%20several%20attendees%20check%20their%20phones%20when%20the%20news%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20does%20have%20massive%20advantages%20in%20scale%20and%20distribution%2C%20thanks%20to%20Android%20and%20Chrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20something%20like%20an%20AI-native%20device%20that%20ditches%20Google's%20ecosystem%20altogether%20eventually%20takes%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20got%20a%20taste%20of%20that%20risk%20last%20month%2C%20when%20the%20stock%20of%20Google's%20parent%20company%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-says-ai-disrupts-search-market-google-impact-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebriefly%20tanked%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Apple%20senior%20vice%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-apple-paid-clicks-eddy-cue-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEddy%20Cue%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20search%20volume%20was%20shrinking%20due%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-highlights-search-giant-ai-momentum-100-updates-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747990802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f3b45c6ad288d1481a510%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-highlights-search-giant-ai-momentum-100-updates-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20I%2FO%20highlights%20include%20100%20AI%20updates%2C%20with%20Gemini%20challengin