about%20what%20could%20have%20been%20but%20knowing%20that%20I%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20become%20an%20unpaid%20interior%20decorator%20for%20a%20man%20in%20his%20mid-30s.%20It%20was%20another%20disappointment%20in%20a%20string%20of%20bad%20dating%20luck.%20An%20ex-boyfriend%20who%20refused%20to%20keep%20his%20apartment%20clean%20told%20me%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20saw%20you%20as%20a%20whole%20person%20for%20the%20first%20time%26quot%3B%20only%20after%20we%20broke%20up.%20An%20attractive%2C%20highly%20educated%2C%20highly%20paid%20consultant%20ghosted%20me%20twice%2C%20telling%20me%20between%20the%20first%20and%20second%20offense%20that%20A)%20the%2040-minute%20subway%20ride%20between%20us%20was%20too%20long%20and%20B)%20he%20had%20experienced%20a%20recent%20glow-up%20and%20was%20feeling%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20attention%20he%20was%20receiving%20from%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it%20wasn't%20just%20bad%20luck.%20At%20happy%20hours%2C%20on%20TikTok%2C%20at%20sociology%20conferences%2C%20and%20in%20the%20board%20rooms%20of%20dating%20app%20companies%2C%20it's%20a%20common%20refrain%20among%20women%2C%20and%20there's%20data%20to%20show%20it%3A%20The%20average%20man%20is%20not%20keeping%20pace%20with%20the%20average%20woman.%20In%201995%2C%20one-quarter%20of%20both%20young%20men%20and%20young%20women%20held%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrowing-trend-fewer-men-in-college-leading-to-mating-crisis-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebachelor's%20degrees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20analysis%20of%20population%20data%20by%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20found.%20The%20analysis%20also%20found%20that%20by%202024%2C%2047%25%20of%20women%20ages%2025%20to%2034%20had%20one%2C%20compared%20with%2037%25%20of%20men.%20Single%20women%20own%202.7%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-single-women-owned-homes-than-single-men-in-2021-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20homes%20in%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20single%20men%2C%20a%20Lending%20Tree%20analysis%20of%20US%20Census%20Bureau%20data%20found.%20Even%20if%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20match%20up%20on%20paper%2C%20the%20social%20divides%20and%20expectations%20between%20them%20can%20make%20partnership%20feel%20uneven.%20In%20couples%20where%20both%20the%20man%20and%20the%20woman%20work%2C%20women%20still%20do%20the%20bulk%20of%20domestic%20labor%20and%20childcare.%20Women%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20men%20to%20seek%20out%20mental%20health%20treatment%20and%20less%20likely%20than%20men%20to%20die%20of%20a%20drug%20overdose%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention.%20Women%20are%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20close%20friends%20with%20whom%20they%20talk%20about%20personal%20topics%20like%20their%20work%2C%20families%2C%20and%20health%20than%20men%2C%20a%202023%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20survey%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20dating%20is%20a%20numbers%20game%2C%20the%20math%20isn't%20adding%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20much%20talk%20of%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmodern-loneliness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emale%20loneliness%20epidemic%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20idea%20that%20men%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20isolated%20and%20lonely%2C%20particularly%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarriage-differences-baby-boomers-millennials-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarriage%20rates%20fall%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20record%20lows.%20There's%20reason%20to%20question%20whether%20men%20really%20are%20lonelier%2C%20as%20a%20recent%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20survey%20found%20that%20men%20and%20women%20reported%20similar%20rates%20of%20loneliness%20but%20that%20women%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20turn%20to%20their%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20or%20mental%20health%20professionals%20for%20emotional%20support.%20Still%2C%20vibe%20shifts%20are%20leading%20some%20young%20men%20to%20turn%20toward%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20content%20creators%20in%20the%20misogynist%20manosphere%20online.%20In%20a%202023%20Survey%20Center%20on%20American%20Life%20survey%2C%20almost%20half%20of%20young%20men%20said%20they%20faced%20discrimination.%20Young%20men%20are%20becoming%20more%20conservative%20as%20young%20women%20become%20more%20liberal.%20All%20this%20mismatch%20is%20frustrating%20the%20remaining%20single%20ladies%20who%20are%20looking%20around%20and%20deciding%20not%20to%20settle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20many%20women%20are%20ready%20to%20throw%20their%20phones%20out%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-south-korea-4b-feminist-movement-trending-after-trump-victory-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswear%20off%20dating%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20winner%20of%20the%20male%20loneliness%20epidemic%20is%20emerging%3A%20men.%20In%20today's%20dating%20world%2C%20men%20who%20are%201)%20employed%20and%202)%20meet%20baseline%20social%20skills%20seem%20to%20be%20cleaning%20up%2C%20having%20their%20pick%20of%20attractive%2C%20successful%2C%20and%20smart%20women%20to%20sort%20through.%20Niko%20Emanuilidis%2C%20a%20dating%20coach%20and%20TikToker%20who%20goes%20under%20the%20name%20The%20Daddy%20Academy%2C%20tells%20me%20that%20while%20many%20men%20have%20turned%20inward%20and%20isolated%20themselves%20amid%20criticism%20of%20men%20and%20masculinity%2C%20those%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20comfortable%20in%20social%20situations%26quot%3B%20and%20confident%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20have%20skyrocketed%20ahead%20of%20all%20the%20rest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20these%20men%20embodying%20what%20Emanuilidis%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bwinner%20effect%26quot%3B%20is%20Jason%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20who%20works%20in%20management%20consulting%20and%20asked%20me%20not%20to%20publish%20his%20last%20name.%20He%20tells%20me%20wants%20to%20meet%20a%20%26quot%3Bnice%20Jewish%20girl%26quot%3B%20and%20settle%20down%2C%20but%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20there%20are%20other%20%26quot%3Bbrilliant%2C%20smart%2C%20funny%2C%20often%20attractive%20women%26quot%3B%20he%20casually%20sees%20amid%20his%20search%20for%20a%20long-term%20relationship.%20He's%20learned%20to%20communicate%20what%20he's%20looking%20for%20in%20both%20serious%20and%20casual%20dating%20situations.%20Jason%20says%20he's%20casually%20seeing%20two%20to%20three%20women%20and%20had%20to%20postpone%20a%20call%20we%20scheduled%20to%20chat%20for%20this%20story%20last%20weekend%20because%2C%20as%20he%20texted%20me%2C%20he%20unexpectedly%20had%20a%20woman%20sleep%20over%20and%20was%20taking%20her%20to%20get%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20rough%20out%20there%2C%20but%20some%20nice%20guys%20with%20jobs%20are%20suddenly%20drowning%20in%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20always%20been%20a%20set%20of%20Most%20Eligible%20Bachelors%2C%20but%20the%20qualifications%20for%20a%20husband%20have%20changed.%20Where%20men%20were%20deemed%20marriage%20material%20for%20their%20income%2C%20and%20women%20for%20domestic%20labor%20and%20child%20rearing%2C%20shifts%20in%20gender%20roles%20are%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20there%20is%20this%20disconnect%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20marriageable%20pool%20that%20isn't%20on%20an%20equal%20footing%20among%20men%20and%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jess%20Carbino%2C%20a%20former%20in-house%20sociologist%20for%20Bumble%20and%20Tinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heterosexual%20women%20I%20spoke%20with%20for%20this%20story%20all%20want%20basically%20the%20same%20general%20thing%3A%20a%20man%20who%20is%20smart%2C%20kind%2C%20and%20emotionally%20intelligent%2C%20and%20has%20friends%20and%20hobbies%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20a%20spark.%20Haleigh%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20who%20works%20in%20marketing%2C%20tells%20me%20she's%20looking%20for%20a%20man%20who's%20employed%2C%20kind%2C%20and%20independent.%20But%20those%20three%20requirements%20increasingly%20feel%20like%20a%20Venn%20diagram%20that's%20hard%20to%20connect%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20always%20have%20to%20pick%20two%20of%20the%20three%3B%20you%20can't%20have%20it%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJana%20K.%20Hoffman%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20writer%2C%20feels%20the%20pool%20of%20men%20who%20meet%20her%20preferences%20is%20small%2C%20particularly%20because%20she%20does%20not%20want%20kids.%20But%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20she%20clicked%20with%20two%20guys%20who%20checked%20her%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20until%20both%20courtships%20fell%20apart%20unexpectedly%20and%20suddenly%2C%20she%20says.%20The%20first%20was%20a%20man%20who%20told%20her%20he%20realized%20he%20actually%20didn't%20want%20%26quot%3Ba%20woman%20with%20her%20shit%20together.%26quot%3B%20The%20second%2C%20after%20about%20a%20month%20of%20dating%2C%20decided%20their%20different%20cuddling%20preferences%20were%20a%20dealbreaker.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20choosing%20these%20very%20strange%20things%20to%20pick%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20tells%20me.%20It's%20been%20sad%20and%20discouraging%2C%20but%20she%20says%20the%20bigger%20problem%20comes%20not%20from%20realizing%20these%20individual%20relationships%20weren't%20going%20to%20pan%20out%20but%20from%20realizing%20it's%20a%20pattern%20that%20makes%20her%20feel%20reluctant%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20again.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20be%20upset%20over%20the%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BNow%20I%20just%20feel%20upset%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mismatch%20problem%20plays%20out%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-dating-apps-changing-new-startups-take-on-tinder-hinge%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20most%20have%20more%20male%20than%20female%20users.%20Women%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20report%20finding%20not%20enough%20%26quot%3Bhigh-quality%26quot%3B%20matches%20and%20getting%20way%20too%20many%20likes%20from%20men%20they%20aren't%20interested%20in%2C%20says%20Chandler%20Willison%2C%20a%20research%20analyst%20at%20the%20research%20and%20analytics%20firm%20M%20Science.%20Many%20men%2C%20conversely%2C%20report%20that%20they%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20crowd%20and%20have%20few%20to%20no%20matches.%20%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20for%20these%20high-value%2C%20highly%20educated%20men%20in%20the%20dating%20marketplace%20outstrips%20the%20supply%2C%20and%20so%20you're%20inevitably%20going%20to%20end%20up%20with%20women%20who%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20be%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20these%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20Willison%20says.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20inevitably%20going%20to%20be%20that%20sort%20of%20mismatch%20between%20the%20men's%20qualifications%20and%20the%20women's%20desires%20at%20large.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20men%20I%20spoke%20with%20for%20this%20story%20are%20going%20on%20lots%20of%20dates%20that%20start%20on%20the%20apps.%20Mo%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20who%20works%20in%20tech%20and%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20serious%20relationship%2C%20has%20his%20dating%20app%20strategy%20solidified%3A%20He%20reopens%20his%20Hinge%20account%20for%20about%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%20and%20then%20works%20through%20the%20matches%20he%20has.%20He%20shifted%20his%20strategy%20after%20continuously%20swiping%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20mid-30s%20and%20found%20that%20he%20passed%20up%20getting%20serious%20with%20some%20great%20women%20because%20he%20was%20wondering%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20there's%20somebody%20better%20than%20who%20I%20just%20met%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20Since%20opening%20up%20Hinge%20in%20the%20past%20month%20after%20getting%20out%20of%20a%20relationship%2C%20Mo%20says%20he%20has%20been%20on%20nine%20first%20dates%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20second%20dates%2C%20and%20already%20has%20one%20woman%20he%20is%20particularly%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20Hinge%20really%20is%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20be%20deleted%26quot%3B%20for%20some%20of%20these%20top-tier%20men.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20point%20of%20a%20date%20is%20to%20have%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20a%20perfect%20match%2C%20he%20usually%20meets%20an%20interesting%20woman.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I've%20ever%20not%20enjoyed%20any%20dates%20that%20I've%20been%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20women%20I%20spoke%20with%20say%20they%20had%20fun%20dating%20in%20their%2020s%20but%20now%20feel%20mostly%20frustrated%20by%20the%20apps.%20There's%20a%20crop%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-dating-startups-and-apps-disrupting-the-industry-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmaller%20alternatives%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Hinge%20and%20Tinder%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20trying%20to%20fix%20that%2C%20but%20they%20still%20run%20into%20vast%20differences%20in%20how%20men%20and%20women%20want%20to%20date.%20On%20Fourplay%2C%20an%20app%20that%20allows%20friends%20to%20date%20in%20pairs%2C%2085%25%20of%20users%20are%20women%2C%20say%20Fourplay's%20cofounders%2C%20Danielle%20Dietzek%20and%20Julie%20Griggs.%20They%20also%20tell%20me%20that%20men%20who%20started%20to%20sign%20up%20but%20never%20added%20a%20friend%20often%20said%20they%20didn't%20have%20a%20single%20guy%20friend%20who%20they%20felt%20comfortable%20seeing%20them%20in%20a%20dating%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20worried%20about%20how%20their%20friend%20would%20act%20on%20a%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20women%20also%20feel%20like%20there's%20confusion%20between%20men%20and%20women%20about%20expectations.%20Emily%20Azrael%2C%20a%20comedian%20and%20writer%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20tells%20me%20that%20she%20once%20dated%20a%20man%20who%20offered%20to%20make%20her%20breakfast%2C%20but%20asked%20for%20her%20credit%20card%20to%20buy%20butter%20%E2%80%94%20since%20she%20would%20be%20the%20one%20keeping%20the%20leftover%20sticks.%20Azrael%20says%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20she's%20not%20on%20the%20same%20page%20as%20men%20on%20dating%20roles%2C%20like%20who%20plans%20a%20first%20date.%20More%20communication%2C%20she%20hopes%2C%20could%20turn%20the%20problem%20around.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20and%20close%20the%20gap%20so%20we%20can%20speak%20the%20same%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20public%20conversations%20about%20the%20gap%20between%20men%20and%20women%20in%20dating%20are%20playing%20out%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20a%20misandrist%20slant%20isn't%20helping.%20If%20you%20scroll%20through%20TikTok%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20find%20women%20who%20say%20they%20hate%20men%20and%20who%20call%20men%20trash.%20There%20are%20dating%20coaches%20who%20give%20black%20and%20white%20advice%2C%20telling%20women%20to%20pull%20back%20and%20manipulate%20men%20into%20chasing%20them.%20They%20give%20broad%2C%20evergreen%20descriptions%20of%20attachment%20styles%20that%20help%20jaded%20daters%20pathologize%20former%20matches%2C%20blurring%20the%20line%20between%20who's%20a%20sadist%20and%20who%20just%20wasn't%20that%20interested%20in%20them.%20People%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20%26quot%3Bengagement%20on%20their%20content%20than%20they%20are%20about%20the%20effect%20that%20content%20will%20have%20on%20the%20greater%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Griggs%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20put%20out%20content%20that%20is%20hating%20on%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20helping%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmanuilidis%20of%20The%20Daddy%20Academy%20thinks%20there%20aren't%20as%20many%20manipulative%2C%20toxic%20guys%20as%20social%20media%20would%20lead%20one%20to%20believe%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ones%20who%20play%20games%20have%20dated%20so%20many%20women%20that%20they%20have%20an%20outsize%20place%20in%20the%20conversation.%20But%20he%20worries%20about%20videos%20and%20posts%20that%20trash-talk%20men.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20group%20of%20men%20who%2C%20their%20winner%20effect%20is%20already%20low%2C%20and%20then%20now%20take%20all%20that%20negativity%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20They%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictim%20mindset%26quot%3B%20and%20turn%20inward%2C%20he%20says%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20male%20role%20models%20online%20that%20are%20speaking%20to%20the%20types%20of%20men.%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Galloway%2C%20whose%20recent%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BNotes%20on%20Being%20a%20Man%2C%26quot%3B%20focuses%20on%20modern%20masculinity%20issues%2C%20has%20a%20similar%20solution%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20need%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20and%20the%20Dow%20to%20hit%20more%20highs%3B%20we%20need%20more%20men%20who%20have%20the%20relationships%20and%20the%20strength%20and%20the%20will%20to%20go%20have%20those%20conversations%20with%20other%20young%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fthe-gray-area%2F390781%2Fmasculinity-scott-galloway-young-men-struggling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20men%20I%20spoke%20with%2C%20dating%20has%20gotten%20more%20fun%2C%20in%20part%20because%20they've%20learned%20to%20be%20candid%20and%20decisive.%20In%20his%2020s%2C%20Jason%20tells%20me%20he%20would%20casually%20date%20and%20hook%20up%20with%20women%20and%20not%20communicate%20his%20intentions%20well.%20It%20led%20to%20drama%20in%20his%20friend%20group%20when%20he%20hurt%20acquaintances'%20feelings%2C%20and%20he%20tells%20me%20dating%20is%20better%20now%20that%20he%20sees%20women%20he%20actually%20likes%20to%20hang%20out%20with%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20just%20casually.%20Now%20he%20lays%20out%20what%20he's%20looking%20for%20early%20on%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20serious%20partnership%20or%20something%20casual.%20He%20says%20he's%20baffled%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20respect%20other%20men%20have%20for%20women.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20fairly%20basic%20thing%3A%20If%20you%20treat%20someone%20with%20respect%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20give%20you%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20naturally%20goes%20positive%20places%20from%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20advice%20for%20guys%20who%20want%20to%20rise%20up%20in%20the%20dating%20pool%20is%20simple%3A%20%26quot%3BBe%20better%2C%20men.%20Get%20her%20a%20bagel%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20hang%20out%20with%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-winners-loneliness-epidemic-nice-guys-with-jobs-dating-apps-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747987981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e2db468a292900801f60a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-winners-loneliness-epidemic-nice-guys-with-jobs-dating-apps-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Good%20men%20are%20harder%20than%20ever%20to%20find.%20Which%20is%20good%20news%20for%20the%20good%20men%20who%20are%20actually%20out%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-winners-loneliness-epidemic-nice-guys-with-jobs-dating-apps-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suicide%20video%2C%20WA%20chats%20from%20man's%20phone%20lead%20to%20FIR%20against%20wife%2C%20lover%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747987847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F