nishing%20my%20dream%20course%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%20With%20Trump's%20crackdown%20on%20foreign%20students%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I'll%20be%20let%20back%20on%20campus.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222659%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreya%20Mishra%20Reddy%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Harvard%20Business%20School%20sign.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682ff5ffc6ad288d1481bb33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221994%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShreya%20Mishra%20Reddy%20has%20one%20module%20to%20go%20to%20complete%20her%20program%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%3Cp%3EShreya%20Mishra%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShreya%20Mishra%20Reddy%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20finishing%20Harvard%20Business%20School's%20Program%20for%20Leadership%20Development.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20block%20Harvard%20from%20enrolling%20foreign%20students%20has%20thrown%20her%20plans%20into%20disarray.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20she%20has%20not%20heard%20from%20the%20university%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Shreya%20Mishra%20Reddy%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20Visa%20technical%20program%20manager%20completing%20Harvard%20Business%20School's%20Program%20for%20Leadership%20Development.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20BI%20has%20verified%20her%20enrollment%20in%20the%20program.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20international%20student%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-business-school-students-launch-class-backed-vc-fund-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Business%20School%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Program%20for%20Leadership%20Development%2C%20and%20I'm%20reeling%20from%20the%20news%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration%20blocking%20Harvard%20from%20enrolling%20foreign%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20from%20India%20in%202021%20to%20do%20my%20master's%20at%20Duke%20University%2C%20and%20then%20got%20my%20dream%20job%20at%20Visa%20in%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20started%20working%20at%20Visa%2C%20I%20came%20across%20this%20program%20at%20Harvard%2C%20which%20is%20an%20alternative%20to%20their%20executive%20MBA.%20I%20applied%20to%20that%20program%2C%20and%20I%20absolutely%20did%20not%20think%20that%20I%20would%20get%20accepted%2C%20but%20I%20did.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20moments%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20my%20parents%2C%20they%20were%20so%20excited.%20I%20went%20from%20being%20a%20first-generation%20immigrant%20in%20the%20US%20to%20being%20accepted%20to%20one%20of%20the%20best%20schools%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f7d09d6-56d0-4ef7-aa02-365d80284475%5C%22%3EThe%20news%20of%20the%20enrollment%20ban%20left%20me%20numb%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20out%20a%20loan%20to%20fund%20the%20%2450%2C000%20tuition%20fee%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20completing%20the%20course.%20I%20just%20have%20one%20module%20left%2C%20from%20May%20to%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20home%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20meeting%20when%20I%20saw%20the%20news%20pop%20up%20on%20my%20phone%20that%20Harvard%20had%20been%20banned%20from%20accepting%20international%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20numb%20for%20a%20minute%20because%20I%20knew%20my%20module%20was%20supposed%20to%20start%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%20and%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20to%20Boston%20in%20July.%20My%20tickets%20are%20all%20booked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20read%20the%20news%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20text%20my%20father%20back%20in%20India%2C%20saying%20that%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20graduate%20from%20Harvard.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20will%20be%20allowed%20back%20on%20campus%20or%20able%20to%20travel%20to%20Boston%20at%20all