t%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENeel%20Soni%20%E2%80%93%20The%2023-year-old%20filmmaker%20from%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Shubhika%20Sharma%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20editor%20of%20%E2%80%98Babli%20By%20Night%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%2C%20who%20is%20Neel%E2%80%99s%20maternal%20aunt%2C%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20his%20journey.%20She%20was%20beaming%20with%20pride%20while%20sharing%20how%20she%20felt%20about%20Neel%E2%80%99s%20achievements%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20proud%20of%20him.%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20film%20when%20it%20was%2058%20minutes%20long%20to%20its%20present%20version%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20witnessed%20his%20toil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoving%20nature%20is%20one%20thing.%20Turning%20that%20love%20into%20a%20film%20that%20also%20captures%20the%20struggles%20of%20the%20queer%20community%20in%20rural%20India%20%E2%80%94%20that%20takes%20something%20deeper.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20decision%20made%20overnight.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20that%20grows%20over%20the%20years%2C%20rooted%20in%20a%20quiet%20devotion%20to%20the%20land%20and%20a%20deep%20belief%20in%20the%20stories%20that%20deserve%20to%20be%20seen%20and%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%2C%20who%20practices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363152%2Fgrow-organic-vegetables-at-home-terrace-garden-homemaker-padma-suresh-income-source%2F%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20herself%20and%20likes%20to%20be%20close%20to%20nature%2C%20candidly%20shares%20one%20of%20her%20fond%20memories%2C%20%E2%80%9CNeel%20and%20I%20started%20going%20to%20the%20forests%20when%20he%20was%20a%20child.%20The%20bond%20that%20we%20share%20today%20is%20because%20of%20wildlife%20and%20nature.%20He%20was%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20old%2C%20and%20we%20were%20at%20our%20farm%20in%20Rajasthan.%20It%20was%20a%20winter%20afternoon%2C%20and%20we%20were%20spending%20time%20in%20the%20greens%20when%20he%20spotted%20a%20bird%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Maasi%2C%20dongo!%E2%80%99%20To%20me%2C%20it%20was%20surprising%20because%20for%20such%20a%20young%20child%20to%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20a%20bird%20by%20its%20name%20was%20out%20of%20the%20blue!%20It%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98drongo%E2%80%99%20bird%20that%20he%20was%20pointing%20at.%20And%20having%20that%20interspersed%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20pronounce%20the%20letter%20%E2%80%98R%E2%80%99%20in%20it%20was%20quite%20adorable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20their%20love%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F432674%2Fwildlife-photographer-sanket-reddy-lessons-nature%2F%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20nature%20conservation%20made%20them%20spend%20myriad%20long%20weekends%20and%20holidays%20in%20nature%E2%80%99s%20lap%2C%20and%20on%20one%20such%20trip%2C%20they%20met%20Babban.%20That%20is%20how%20the%20story%20that%20was%20hidden%20in%20the%20canopy%20of%20societal%20norms%20and%20waited%20for%20years%20to%20be%20heard%20found%20its%20footing%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20predilection%20for%20the%20greens.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%20also%20highlights%20that%20the%20documentary%20has%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20her%20and%20how%20she%20now%20feels%20toward%20the%20queer%20community%20%E2%80%94%20compassion%2C%20love%2C%20and%20acknowledgment%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20all%20are%20humans!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20forest%20trails%20to%20BAFTA%20longlist%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%E2%80%99re%20working%20on%20something%20you%20truly%20care%20about%2C%20the%20growth%20you%20experience%20goes%20far%20beyond%20anything%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20in%20books.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20felt%20this%20deeply.%20Telling%20untold%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F421780%2Fwildlife-documentari