v%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hidden%20emergency%20in%20our%20breath%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20knock%20on%20your%20door.%20It%20seeps%20in%20quietly%E2%80%94through%20windows%2C%20lungs%2C%20and%20childhoods.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20contributes%20to%20nearly%20one%20in%20every%20ten%20deaths.%20During%20my%20PhD%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20groups%E2%80%94babies%20in%20prams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20findings%20were%20startling%3A%20children%20in%20prams%20are%20exposed%20to%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollutants%20than%20adults.%20Their%20breathing%20height%20puts%20them%20right%20in%20line%20with%20vehicle%20exhaust.%20Some%20children%20face%20up%20to%2072%25%20higher%20pollution%20levels%20simply%20based%20on%20where%20they%20sit%20in%20a%20double%20pram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20knowledge%20alone%20isn%E2%80%99t%20power.%20Action%20is.%20So%20we%20created%20practical%2C%20scalable%20interventions%E2%80%94pram%20covers%2C%20urban%20route%20mapping%2C%20low-cost%20sensors%E2%80%94and%20tested%20them%20in%20real-world%20conditions.%20The%20Mitigating%20Air%20Pollution%20Exposure%20(MAPE)%20project%2C%20funded%20by%20UKRI%2C%20was%20not%20just%20a%20research%20study.%20It%20became%20a%20guide%20for%20urban%20parents%20navigating%20toxic%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20insights%20shaped%20public%20conversations%2C%20infor